sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936485b5dd9c0eb30b24f471510a3a987d4121cd","tid":614863,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3b79d482f085b722c64dca2166b6e25b26efbc","tid":614863,"uid":91152,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"學車真係好貴 學自動波跟師傅要一萬 <br />\n棍波要多五千 我又想一take pass <br />\n新車聽上面講又多數自動波<br />\n阿sir第一堂就唔鼓勵我學棍波 <br />\n我諗我都係死死地氣認垃圾學自動波算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"駕院學都棍/自都係一樣$10,990<br />\n你都幾矛盾 唔想肥又自認廢 但就報街師傅<br />\n明明駕院泊車調頭一定易過出面 路試就一樣合格率(運吉處有stat睇)<br />\n你鍾意啦你開心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}